<main class="wc-screen ">
  <div class="top-art" aria-hidden="true">
    <img class="hero-title" src="../../assets/football/home/hero-title-figma.webp" alt="">
  </div>
  <section class="modal-layer" aria-label="分享活动弹窗">
    <div class="dialog">
      <span class="pill-label">分享活动</span>
      <button class="close-circle" aria-label="关闭"></button>
      <h1>邀请好友一起助威</h1>
      <p>跳转到分享页面即可增加 1 次抽奖机会，每人每天最多额外获得 5 次。</p>
      <div class="action-row">
        <button class="primary-btn">分享给好友</button>
        <button class="secondary-btn">分享朋友圈</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
